            </ul>
            <a
              href="javascript:;"
              class="py-2.5 px-5 bg-accent shadow-sm rounded-full transition-all duration-500 text-base text-white text-center w-fit block mx-auto hover:bg-indigo-700"
              >Išbandyti</a
